{"tid":220368,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"外籍男俾女偷錢好躁火 酒店呱呱嘈","createTime":"2017-04-28T01:57:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-28T02:17:13.000Z","uid":73262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d81b4753e07d131b451d8dacd18d5313bf1be18d","tid":220368,"uid":73262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T01:57:00.000Z","msg":"灣仔駱克道57-73號香港華美粵海酒店，凌晨零時許，一名35歲外籍男遊客，向職員報稱被一名女子偷錢，職員到走廊發現他情緒激動，並扭傷腳踝，職員扶他入房間協助包紮及報警，其後送院治理。<br />\n<br />\n約1個多小時後他返回酒店，又聲稱被職員毆打，要求賠償，與職員發生爭執，並用啤酒潑向地上，以及報警求助。<br />\n<br />\n據稱，該名外籍男遊客偕同一名女子返酒店房間，其後發覺被偷錢，追出時扭傷腳。他送院後又拒絕治療，並對事件不追究，<span style=\"color: red;\">自行返回酒店及飲啤酒</span>，疑有醉意與職員爭吵及潑酒。警方翻查閉路電視，沒有發現外籍男被職員毆打，案件列糾紛處理。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56623937&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170428\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56623937%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170428&d=ulKCtXgG4rwmRR8qyGKIuVeK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=a90de9e2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56623937%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170428&h=e9997ef2\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56623937&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170428</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/g92weuvx\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fg92weuvx&h=e5c53a4e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5d9e57914a27a4b423e5361ef9e7f37f2a4b032a","tid":220368,"uid":26978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T02:02:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 俾ptgf偷錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/nor